    "en": {
      "title": "May 9 violence - 14 more arrested",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Another 14 people have been arrested in connection with the attacks on the Kota Ko Kama and Maina Ko Kama protesters and the violence and unrest.",
        "Also, 3,056 people have been arrested in connection with the said 857 incidents, out of which 1,150 people have been remanded."
      ],
